WarpCTC的安装和简单使用

git clone https://github.com/SeanNaren/warp-ctc.git
cd warp-ctc
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
cd pytorch_binding
python setup.py install

针对 Error 1:
cmake ..
make

[ 20%] Building CXX object CMakeFiles/warpctc.dir/src/ctc_entrypoint.cpp.o
clang: error: unsupported option '-fopenmp'

解决方案连接
https://blog.csdn.net/xhzDeng/article/details/80511437

--解决方案
cd build/CMakeCache.txt

更改配置为
//compile warp-ctc with openmp.
// ON -> OFF
WITH_OMP:BOOL=OFF


1、安装cmake
https://blog.csdn.net/fanyun_01/article/details/102332894
1.1、下载：curl -O https://cmake.org/files/v3.6/cmake-3.6.0-Linux-x86_64.tar.gz
1.2、解压：tar -zxvf cmake-3.6.0-Linux-x86_64.tar.gz（不是源码包，解压后直接使用）。
1.3、增加环境变量，使其成为全局变量：
第一种方法:
vim /etc/profile
export PATH=$PATH:/lnmp/src/cmake-3.6.0-Linux-x86_64/bin


echo $PATH
cmake --version


2、opencv的编译
下载opencv:https://github.com/opencv/opencv.git

解压之后
cd opencv-x-xx
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../
make
make install

3、处理opencv的配置问题
http://t.zoukankan.com/wuyuan2011woaini-p-15748668.html
cd /usr/local/lib
sudo mkdir pkgconfig
cd pkgconfig
sudo touch opencv.pc

vim opencv.pc
再打开opencv.pc文件，文件内输入：（监测对应路径是否存在）
------------------------填入如下内容

prefix=/usr/local
exec_prefix=${prefix}
includedir=${prefix}/include
libdir=${exec_prefix}/lib

Name: opencv
Description: The opencv library
Version:4.1.2
Cflags: -I${includedir}/opencv4
Libs: -L${libdir} -lopencv_stitching -lopencv_objdetect  -lopencv_calib3d -lopencv_features2d
-lopencv_highgui -lopencv_videoio -lopencv_imgcodecs -lopencv_video -lopencv_photo -lopencv_ml
-lopencv_imgproc -lopencv_flann  -lopencv_core

--------

export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=/usr/local/lib/pkgconfig
